long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
Alternative Frontends - Open Source Browser Extension

This extension redirects popular websites to their privacy-respecting alternatives. Works for embedded YouTube videos too.

No malicious JavaScript or Cookies. No ads and no tracking. No distractions, just browsing.

What is a Frontned?
Frontend (also spelled "Front End") - part of a software program or a website with which the user interacts. It is synonymous with the user interface.

Currently supported websites:
- Twitter
- YouTube
- Reddit
- Instagram
- Google Search
- Google Maps
- Wikipedia
